冠肺炎檢測計劃。此外，華昇診斷中心亦為未來在香港發展健康碼系統做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n聽日不問價柯煙8037<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">唔好比佢地再spin過去玩送中碼，邊個再講就剷佢地叫返佢地搞防疫衛生認證！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n20蚊張同建制唔該唔好再推個責任比人，餐廳商場應該攞「衛生碼」，唔係要人攞送中碼食飯！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162097\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162097</a>"},{"pid":"4962cc812d0821b0f9fb53c488dadb72a4372d28","tid":2161534,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"264b882a585d962866b216222a83868757877580","tid":2161534,"uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"仆你個街<br />\n佢母公司係咪搞新疆健康碼個間？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">唔好比佢地再spin過去玩送中碼，邊個再講就剷佢地叫返佢地搞防疫衛生認證！<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n20蚊張同建制唔該唔好再推個責任比人，餐廳商場應該攞「衛生碼」，唔係要人攞送中碼食飯！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2162097\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2162097</a>"},{"pid":"39a887c879e3dbdb138eb3d7b345e0d940d68ff2","tid":2161534,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"食屎啦送中碼"},{"pid":"03132a64992a0762f49caa43809a50cb7de99e28","tid":2161534,"uid":8170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:56:19.000Z","msg":"一日得 13萬咁少？明明武漢一千萬人，幾日就驗晒㗎喎。"},{"pid":"962816120e2a908dcfd6e4eccfba8ec7feabf913","tid":2161534,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db1ebc41ce3f982e2ee38b9aa4fb6bfe686dac8","tid":2161534,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:01:59.000Z",